<para style="p">For the chief musician. A psalm of David; to bring to remembrance.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Save me, God!</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh, come quickly and help me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Let those who try to take my life</para>

<para style="q1">be ashamed and humiliated;</para>

<para style="q1">let them be turned back and brought to dishonor,</para>

<para style="q1">those who take pleasure in my pain.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Let them be turned back because of their shame,</para>

<para style="q1">those who say, "Aha, aha."</para>
